    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduo a MessagePack Module</title>

      <para>
        <application>MessagePack</application> is an efficient binary serialization
format. It lets you exchange data among multiple languages like JSON. But
it's faster and smaller. This package provides CPython bindings for reading
and writing MessagePack data.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

